text: Greatest Hits is the first greatest hits album by American singer-songwriter Jewel. The album was released on February 5, 2013 and features duets from Kelly Clarkson and the Pistol Annies. ==Track listing== ==Chart performance== {| class="wikitable sortable" |- ! Chart (2013) !
